@startuml Builder Pattern Test - Computer

title 建造者模式测试示例 - 电脑配置

class Computer {
    - cpu: String
    - ram: String
    - ssd: String
    - gpu: String
    - Computer(builder: Builder)
    + toString(): String
}

class Builder {
    - cpu: String
    - ram: String
    - ssd: String
    - gpu: String
    + Builder(cpu: String)
    + buildRAM(ram: String): Builder
    + buildSSD(ssd: String): Builder
    + buildGPU(gpu: String): Builder
    + build(): Computer
}

Computer +-- Builder : 内部类

Builder ..> Computer : 创建

note right of Computer
  产品类
  包含多个组件
end note

note right of Builder
  建造者(内部类)
  使用链式调用
  构建Computer对象
end note

note bottom of Builder
  示例用法：
  Computer computer = new Computer.Builder("Intel i7")
      .buildRAM("16GB")
      .buildSSD("512GB")
      .buildGPU("RTX 3060")
      .build();
end note

@enduml
